lead_paragraph: Victoria Azarenka of Belarus routed Naomi Osaka of Japan, 6-1, 6-1, and the path in her draw became easier when Garbiñe Muguruza was upset by Barbora Strycova, 6-3, 6-2.

headline.print_headline: Azarenka Advances to Round of 16; Third-Ranked Muguruza Is Ousted
headline.main: Azarenka Advances to Round of 16; Third-Ranked Muguruza Is Ousted
